flowchart LR
  subgraph UI[Frontend - Vue / Wails]
    A[Dashboard]
    B[Reader]
    C[Quiz]
    D[Flashcards]
    E[Socratic Tutor]
    F[Settings]
  end

  subgraph Backend[Go + Wails Backend]
    G[API Command Handler]
    H[Notebook Ingestion]
    I[RAG Pipeline]
    J[Scheduler / FSRS]
    K[LLM Provider Adapter]
    L[Embedding Runtime]
  end

  subgraph Data[Local Storage]
    M[SQLite DB]
    N[sqlite-vec Vector Index]
    O[Assets: tokenizer.json, model_int8.onnx]
  end

  A -->|send command| G
  B -->|send command| G
  C -->|send command| G
  D -->|send command| G
  E -->|send command| G
  F -->|send command| G

  G -->|read/write| M
  G -->|query vectors| N
  G -->|load assets| O
  G -->|call external API| K
  G -->|compute embeddings| L

  subgraph Ingest[Notebook Upload / Ingestion]
    U[Upload PDF/TXT/MD]
    V[Extract document sections]
    W[Detect chapters/topics]
    X[Chunk & parent section creation]
    Y[Generate embeddings]
  end

  U --> V --> W --> X --> Y
  X -->|store metadata| M
  Y -->|store embeddings| N
  Y --> L
  O --> L

  subgraph Learn[Study Flows]
    Q[Ask AI / Explain]
    R[Quiz generation]
    S[Flashcard review]
  end

  Q --> G
  R --> G
  S --> G
  G --> J
  J --> M

